      • getSummary

        public ServiceCall<Summary> getSummary(File imagesFile)
        Upload a set of images as a ZIP file for visual insight extraction.
        Here is the code to get the Summary of a collection of images: 
         VisualInsights service = new VisualInsights();
 service.setUsernameAndPassword("<username>", "<password>");
 
 File images = new File("images.zip");
 Summary summary = service.getSummary(images).execute();
 
 System.out.println(summary);
        Parameters:
        imagesFile - the images File
        Returns:
        the Summary of the collection's visual attributes
